				"id": "t3_7",
				"text": "<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Grupp</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Substanser</strong></div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Opiater och </span></div><div class=\"tableLine\">opioider<a class=\"tableFootnoteLink\" href=\"#fnote_13\"><sup>a</sup></a></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1047632\"></a>Morfin, heroin, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1047633\"></a>råopium, <br></div><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1047635\"></a>kodein, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1047636\"></a>metadon, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1047637\"></a>petidin, </div><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1047638\"></a>etylmorfin,<a class=\"index\" id=\"1047639\"></a> ketobemidon, </div><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1047640\"></a>buprenorfin, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1047641\"></a>dextropropoxi-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">fen, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1047642\"></a>tramadol, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1047643\"></a>fentanyl</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-family: &apos;Avenir Next&apos;, &apos;Helvetica Neue Ultra Light&apos;, &apos;Helvetica Neue&apos;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Sedativa/hypnotika</span></div><div class=\"tableLine\"></div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Alkohol</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1040037\"></a>Etanol, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040038\"></a>metanol, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040039\"></a>kloral-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">hydrat </div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1040042\"></a>Barbiturater</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1040045\"></a>Metohexital, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040046\"></a>pentotal, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040047\"></a>fene-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">mal, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040049\"></a>meprobamat</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Benso-<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">diazepiner</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1040053\"></a>Diazepam, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040054\"></a>klordiazepoxid,<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1040056\"></a>klonazepam, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040057\"></a>lorazepam,<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1040058\"></a>alprazolam, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040059\"></a>midazolam,<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1040060\"></a>oxazepam, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040061\"></a>nitrazepam,<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1040062\"></a>flunitrazepam, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040063\"></a>triazolam </div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Övriga</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1040067\"></a>Zolpidem, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040068\"></a>zopiklon, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040069\"></a>zale-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">plon, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040071\"></a>klometiazol</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">3. Central-</span></div><div class=\"tableLine\">stimulantia</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1043644\"></a>Amfetamin, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1043645\"></a>metamfetamin, <br></div><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1043647\"></a>fenmetrazin, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1043649\"></a>metylfenidat,<a class=\"index\" id=\"1043650\"></a> <a class=\"index\" id=\"1043651\"></a></div><div class=\"tableLine\">ecstasy (MDMA), <a class=\"index\" id=\"1043652\"></a>khat (<a class=\"index\" id=\"1043653\"></a>quat, </div><div class=\"tableLine\">qat, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1043654\"></a>tschat, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1043655\"></a>miraa)</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">4. Kokain</span></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1040090\"></a>Kokain, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040091\"></a>crack, ”free-base”</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">5. <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040094\"></a>Cannabinoider</span></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1040097\"></a>Hasch, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040098\"></a>marijuana</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">6. Hallucino-</span></div><div class=\"tableLine\">gener</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1040103\"></a>LSD, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040104\"></a>meskalin, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040105\"></a>psilocybin </div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"footNotes\"><div class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_13\"><strong>a.</strong> <div class=\"tableLine\">”Opiater” refererar till narkotiska alkaloider utvunna ur </div><div class=\"tableLine\">opium, t ex morfin och kodein, eller derivat av dessa alka-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">loider, t ex heroin. ”Opioider” refererar till medel som inte </div><div class=\"tableLine\">är opiater, men har liknande farmakologiska effekter, t ex </div><div class=\"tableLine\">syntetiska substanser som ketobemidon, eller endogena opi-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">oida peptider som enkefalin.</div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>"
